title: Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea S04E20 Man-Beast
description:
Voyage to the Bottom of the Sea

S04E20
Man-Beast

Airdate: February 18, 1968

- One of 26 episodes from Season Four which are not yet on DVD
- Remastered audio and video from VHS - Excellent quality!
- Contains two additional scenes not shown on cable TV!

The Seaview's crew deals with a Jekyll-Hyde crisis: Crane (David Hedison) is periodically changing into a raving monster.

Nelson: Richard Basehart. Morton: Bob Dowdell. Kowalski: Del Monroe. Sharkey: Terry Becker. Braddock: Lawrence Montaigne.
